---
import LandingSegmentLayout from "../layouts/LandingSegmentLayout.astro";
---

<LandingSegmentLayout>
  <div class="py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-sm font-mono tracking-wider mb-6">
        OUR METHODOLOGY
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        From Vision to<br />
        <span class="gradient-text">Production Intelligence</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
        We don't just build systems—we architect custom analytics tools that evolve with your organization. Our methodology ensures rapid iteration, continuous improvement, and measurable business impact.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <!-- Phase 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl font-mono">
              01
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Discovery & Architecture</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We start by understanding your data landscape, business objectives, and technical constraints. Through workshops, data audits, and stakeholder interviews, we map your current state and design the target unified architecture.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 font-light">
              <li>• Data source inventory & assessment</li>
              <li>• Stakeholder requirement gathering</li>
              <li>• Technical architecture design</li>
              <li>• Proof-of-concept development</li>
              <li>• Risk assessment & mitigation planning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl font-mono">
              02
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Data Integration & Pipeline Development</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We build the foundational data layer, connecting all your sources into a unified pipeline. This includes ETL/ELT processes, data quality checks, schema evolution, and real-time streaming capabilities.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 font-light">
              <li>• Data pipeline architecture & implementation</li>
              <li>• Schema design & normalization</li>
              <li>• Data quality monitoring & validation</li>
              <li>• Real-time streaming infrastructure</li>
              <li>• Data lineage & documentation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl font-mono">
              03
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Spatial-Temporal Model Development</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We develop custom spatial and time series models tailored to your specific use cases. This includes temporal feature engineering, spatial data preparation, forecasting model training, validation, and deployment into production inference pipelines.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 font-light">
              <li>• Time series feature engineering & preparation</li>
              <li>• Spatial pattern analysis & clustering</li>
              <li>• Forecasting model training & validation</li>
              <li>• Geographic intelligence model development</li>
              <li>• A/B testing frameworks for temporal models</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 4 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl font-mono">
              04
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Application & Interface Development</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We build the interfaces that make your analytics tools accessible—custom dashboards, APIs, visualization tools, and natural language query interfaces that enable decision-makers to interact with the system.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 font-light">
              <li>• User experience design & prototyping</li>
              <li>• Dashboard & visualization development</li>
              <li>• API design & implementation</li>
              <li>• Natural language query interfaces</li>
              <li>• Mobile & responsive design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 5 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl font-mono">
              05
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Deployment & Production Operations</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We deploy your system to production with full observability, monitoring, and automated scaling. This includes CI/CD pipelines, infrastructure as code, security hardening, and operational runbooks.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 font-light">
              <li>• Infrastructure provisioning & configuration</li>
              <li>• CI/CD pipeline setup</li>
              <li>• Monitoring & alerting systems</li>
              <li>• Security hardening & compliance</li>
              <li>• Documentation & training</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 6 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-2xl font-mono">
              06
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Continuous Improvement & Evolution</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Analytics tools are living systems. We establish feedback loops, model retraining pipelines, and continuous monitoring to ensure your system improves over time and adapts to changing conditions.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2 font-light">
              <li>• Performance monitoring & optimization</li>
              <li>• Model retraining & updates</li>
              <li>• Feature expansion & enhancement</li>
              <li>• User feedback integration</li>
              <li>• Strategic roadmap planning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 bg-gray-900 text-white p-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
          Agile, Iterative, Results-Driven
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
          We don't wait until the end to show value. Our methodology delivers working data capabilities in weeks, not months. Each phase builds on the previous one, ensuring continuous progress and early validation of assumptions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</LandingSegmentLayout>

